{"tid":2067752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"郭偉健 蘇偉德 彭寶琴 張潔宜 蘇文隆","createTime":"2020-06-17T08:10:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-23T05:15:06.000Z","uid":277037,"like":42,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"84b22a060cb3ac4286340252fb747a7a20d99c0a","tid":2067752,"uid":277037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T08:10:13.000Z","msg":"郭偉健<br />\n蘇偉德<br />\n彭寶琴<br />\n張潔宜<br />\n錢禮<br />\n胡雅文<br />\n嚴舜儀<br />\n吳重儀<br />\n香淑孄<br />\n蘇文隆<br />\n<br />\n我會定期出一個紅官post同定時更新，最後輸就輸，反正爛命一條，但贏嘅話你地班紅官唔駛旨意走得甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n歡迎大家一齊貼佢地嘅威水史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fc1bf2d48b9015f637ddabe35936fa6e203eea4","tid":2067752,"uid":26014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T08:10:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9f217f21e2f927abc9fb39aab5af25190fbb2dd","tid":2067752,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T08:11:19.000Z","msg":"有無人制裁佢地？"},{"pid":"99d473c1a68e6c633a0bee28f2b8daa5137848ed","tid":2067752,"uid":103156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T08:11:45.000Z","msg":"公敵"},{"pid":"fccbdd76f9078c10e3c5d478a677675f4c3bb126","tid":2067752,"uid":277037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b9f217f21e2f927abc9fb39aab5af25190fbb2dd","tid":2067752,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T08:11:19.000Z","msg":"有無人制裁佢地？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T08:12:04.000Z","msg":"寧可信其有 不可信其無"},{"pid":"3d86185be44e90ab6c0e44185a7ddcd20c9e9eea","tid":2067752,"uid":277037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T08:13:35.000Z","msg":"貼一下事績先<br />\n社工復興運動成員、註冊社工劉家棟於去年7月27日元朗示威中，身處推進中的警察防線前，要求警方讓人群慢慢散去，被控阻差辦公，案件經審訊後，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">蘇文隆</span></span>署理主任裁判官裁定被告罪成，並即判囚一年。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大律師李安然曾於結案陳詞時指，本案是由誤會造成，被告當時似想與警方溝通，但被誤會成想阻礙警方及故意推撞防線。他指傳媒片段拍到持圓盾警員推撞被告，才會令被告撞向由持長盾警員築成的防線，及後更被推入防線之後；另外亦有其他警員推被告，令被告身不由己、不由自主地移動。"},{"pid":"d4925c4afe5dd04a4105d92d81470a49bd9abcf6","tid":2067752,"uid":128763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T08:14:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"038c1e80bef0f90da18b8c8669a95d471ed52366","tid":2067752,"uid":124113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T08:14:58.000Z","msg":"關錢禮咩事？"},{"pid":"ba62fe436cd0c9d37600c5dca7ae9b13b089581a","tid":2067752,"uid":293227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T08:17:06.000Z","msg":"呢啲list 真係要keep 好佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"201f0f26deb8dd03a598b716c169f7f6e858b98c","tid":2067752,"uid":32675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T08:30:03.000Z","msg":"當個list長到成三十個,成本就變咗一條命只係同阻差辦工一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a555ecb916b43267be9e5379f6b12720b95d9ca5","tid":2067752,"uid":277037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"038c1e80bef0f90da18b8c8669a95d471ed52366","tid":2067752,"uid":124113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T08:14:58.000Z","msg":"關錢禮咩事？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-17T08:33:00.000Z","msg":"錢禮唔閪？"},{"pid":"1d516d97bedd338b68233c0b453e59912f8d5ef6","tid":2067752,"uid":118716,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-